== 外界批评 ==
对于沃尔玛的批评，主要集中在于其破坏[[传统|传统]][[社区|社区]]生活方式，对于[[环境|环境]]的破坏，反对工会、对于员工的[[剥削|剥削]]以及在诸如[[中国大陸|中国大陸]]和[[印尼|印尼]]等地开设“[[血汗工厂|血汗工厂]]”等方面，这些在一部名为《沃尔玛：低价格的高代价》的纪录片中有较详尽的介绍。

沃尔玛是众多群众和团体批评的对象。其中[[工会|工会]]、社区群体、[[草根|草根]]组织、[[宗教|宗教]]团体、[[环保|环保]]组织都明确主张反对沃尔玛集团的公司政策、运作手段，甚至是消费该集团商品或服务的消费者。<ref name="mkabel">Kabel, Marcus. "[http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/18/AR2006071800981.html Wal-Mart, Critics Slam Each Other on Web] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/18/AR2006071800981.html |date=20110628232648 }}." ''[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]].'' July 18, 2006. Retrieved on July 31, 2006.</ref><ref>Sellers, Jeff M.（April 22, 2005）. "[http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/116/52.0.html Women Against Wal-Mart] {{Wayback|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/116/52.0.html |date=20081121092201 }}." ''[[Christianity_Today|Christianity Today]].'' Retrieved July 31, 2006.</ref><ref>Sellers, Jeff M.（April 22, 2005）. "[http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/005/17.40.html Deliver Us from Wal-Mart?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/005/17.40.html |date=20081013214512 }}." ''[[Christianity_Today|Christianity Today]].''. Retrieved on July 31, 2006.</ref>而在国际采购、产品供应、环保措施、贸易补贴的使用以及劳工[[福利|福利]]政策等也有批评的声音。<ref>Norman, Al (2004). "The Case Against Wal-Mart". Raphel Marketing, p. 7. [[Special:Booksources/0971154236|ISBN 0-9711542-3-6]].</ref>沃尔玛否认了批评，认为自己毫无过错，超市商品与服务能以低价出售是因为公司运作效率高。<ref>Copeland, Larry.（March 13, 2006）. "[http://www.usatoday.com/money/companies/2006-03-15-young-walmart-usat_x.htm Wal-Mart's hired advocate takes flak] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/companies/2006-03-15-young-walmart-usat_x.htm |date=20120905062401 }}." ''[[USA_Today|USA Today]].'' Retrieved on July 31, 2006.</ref><ref>Rodino Associates.（October 28, 2003）. "[http://www.lacity.org/council/cd13/houscommecdev/cd13houscommecdev239629107_04262005.pdf Final Report on Research for Big Box Retail/Superstore Ordinance] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326214712/http://www.lacity.org/council/cd13/houscommecdev/cd13houscommecdev239629107_04262005.pdf |date=2009-03-26 }}." ''[[Los_Angeles|Los Angeles City Council]].'' Retrieved on July 31, 2006.</ref><ref>Smith, Hedrick. "[http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/walmart/secrets/shots.html Who Calls the Shots in the Global Economy?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/walmart/secrets/shots.html |date=20210410192847 }}" ''[[Public_Broadcasting_Service|PBS]].'' Retrieved on July 31, 2006.</ref>

在2005年，为了能利用自身的影响力去影响大众抵制沃尔玛，工会新设立了一些组织、创办了一些网站用于加强宣传。这其中包括了覺悟吧沃尔玛（{{link-en|Wake Up Wal-Mart|Wake Up Wal-Mart}}）、沃尔玛围观团（{{link-en|Wal-Mart Watch|Wal-Mart Watch}}）。

